item.title: CVE-2023-33175|2023-05-30T04:31:36.503Z -- mubarakalmehairbi -- toui
item.description: ToUI is a Python package for creating user interfaces (websites and desktop apps) from HTML. ToUI is using Flask-Caching (SimpleCache) to store user variables. Websites that use `Website.user_vars` property. It affects versions 2.0.1 to 2.4.0. This issue has been patched in version 2.4.1.
